about.summary: Bash completion for the conda commmand.

name: conda-bash-completion
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "conda-bash-completion" %}
{% set version = "1.5" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/tartansandal/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 82fa38dae6cec42095b5a1f82d5db41b35a7a2c35642a9b7ad548385ae601659

build:
  number: 0
  skip: True  # [win or osx]

requirements:
  run:
    - bash-completion

test:
  source_files:
    - conda
  requires:
    - bash >=4.1
  commands:
    # Ensure the library loads without error
    - bash -e conda

about:
  home: https://github.com/tartansandal/conda-bash-completion
  license: GPL3
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Bash completion for the conda commmand."

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tartansandal
